@OrigamAI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5244

### Smoke-test: Origam community public API
GET https://community.origam.com/categories.json
Accept: application/json

### Ingest a manual chunk
POST {{OrigamAI_HostAddress}}/api/rag/ingest-text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "manual-1",
  "text": "Origam is a low-code platform for building data-driven business applications.",
  "tags": { "source": "manual" }
}

### Ingest topics from all Origam community categories
POST {{OrigamAI_HostAddress}}/api/rag/ingest-origam?maxTopicsPerCategory=5

### Ingest from a single category
POST {{OrigamAI_HostAddress}}/api/rag/ingest-origam?categoryId=5&maxTopicsPerCategory=20

### Ask the RAG
POST {{OrigamAI_HostAddress}}/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How do I configure authentication in Origam?",
  "filter": "source=origam-community"
}

### Vector search (no LLM)
GET {{OrigamAI_HostAddress}}/api/rag/search?q=authentication&limit=5

###
